This is my 2nd visit to Cha Da in just over 24hrs! I came here for lunch and ordered the Special Pho #2 with roast pork, Chinese broccoli and thin rice noodles. I ordered the spice medium which was as hot as I could handle. The broth was so tasty and for a Thai restaurant, this was absolutely the best Pho I have ever had. It's also what drew me back once again. I am sure their other dishes are equally excellent. I will be back again very soon.

